title: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems
description: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems this is inred text.
OB: When choosing the project name as 'test' in the Copy Project dialog, a static text validation error appears.
EB: The Copy Project dialog should not display a static text validation error when choosing the project name as 'test'.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the Copy Project dialog.
2. Enter 'test' as the project name.
3. Observe the static text validation error.
